                "controls": true,
                "volume": 0.5
            }
        },
        {
            "_id": "e76b9913ebcd1bab",
            "_key": "!journal.pages!31bbf83392ea17cc.e76b9913ebcd1bab",
            "_stats": {
                "compodiumSource": null,
                "coreVersion": "12.327",
                "createdTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "duplicateSource": null,
                "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y",
                "modifiedTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "systemId": "dc20rpg",
                "systemVersion": "0.8.0"
            },
            "flags": {},
            "image": {},
            "name": "Heroic Taunt",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 11,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to attempt to Taunt all enemies within 5 Spaces. Make an Attack Check or Intimidation Check (your choice) contested by each target\u2019s Mental Save. <strong>Contest </strong> <strong>Success:</strong> Each creature you beat is <strong>Taunted</strong> (DisADV on Attack and Spell Checks against creatures other than you) by you until the end of your next turn.</p><p><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong> <strong><em>Legendary Taunt:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>2 SP</strong> to have any damage dealt by enemies Taunted by this Technique to be halved against creatures other than you.</p>",
                "format": 1
            },
            "title": {
                "level": 3,
                "show": true
            },
            "type": "text",
            "video": {
                "controls": true,
                "volume": 0.5
            }
        },
        {
            "_id": "7ac485a6c6a9376f",
            "_key": "!journal.pages!31bbf83392ea17cc.7ac485a6c6a9376f",
            "_stats": {
                "compodiumSource": null,
                "coreVersion": "12.327",
                "createdTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "duplicateSource": null,
                "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y",
                "modifiedTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "systemId": "dc20rpg",
                "systemVersion": "0.8.0"
            },
            "flags": {},
            "image": {},
            "name": "Slip Away",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 12,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p><strong><em>Trigger:</em></strong> A creature misses you with an Attack.</p><p><strong><em>Reaction:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to take the Full Dodge Action and move up to your Speed.</p><p><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong> <strong><em>Diving Attack:</em></strong> You can spend<strong> 1 SP</strong> to make an Attack Check against a creature within 1 Space of you as part of Slip Away (you make this attack before the creature makes theirs).</p>",
                "format": 1
            },
            "title": {
                "level": 3,
                "show": true
            },
            "type": "text",
