            }
        },
        {
            "_id": "71dc68115997f9f4",
            "_key": "!journal.pages!31bbf83392ea17cc.71dc68115997f9f4",
            "_stats": {
                "compodiumSource": null,
                "coreVersion": "12.327",
                "createdTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "duplicateSource": null,
                "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y",
                "modifiedTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "systemId": "dc20rpg",
                "systemVersion": "0.8.0"
            },
            "flags": {},
            "image": {},
            "name": "Sunder Armor",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 13,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to make an Attack Check against a creature with Damage Reduction (DR). You deal additional damage equal to the target\u2019s PDR value. This damage ignores the target\u2019s PDR.</p><p><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong> <strong><em>Armor Shred:</em></strong> You can spend<strong> 1 SP</strong> to further increase the damage done by an amount equal to the target's PDR.</p><p><strong><em>Broken Armor: </em></strong>You can spend <strong>1 SP</strong> to reduce the PD of the target by 2 for the rest of the Combat. A creature can\u2019t be affected by this again until the effect ends.</p>",
                "format": 1
            },
            "title": {
                "level": 3,
                "show": true
            },
            "type": "text",
            "video": {
                "controls": true,
                "volume": 0.5
            }
        },
        {
            "_id": "18b38a14b58ac7eb",
            "_key": "!journal.pages!31bbf83392ea17cc.18b38a14b58ac7eb",
            "_stats": {
                "compodiumSource": null,
                "coreVersion": "12.327",
                "createdTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "duplicateSource": null,
                "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y",
                "modifiedTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "systemId": "dc20rpg",
                "systemVersion": "0.8.0"
            },
            "flags": {},
            "image": {},
            "name": "Tumble and Dive",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 14,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p><strong><em>Trigger:</em></strong> You\u2019re the target of an Attack.</p><p><strong><em>Reaction:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP </strong>to move up to your Speed and avoid the attack entirely as long as you end your movement outside of the range or behind Full Cover of the Attack. This movement provokes Opportunity Attacks as normal.</p><p><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong> <strong><em>Heroic Dive:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>2 SP</strong> to bring a willing creature within 1 Space along with you as part of Tumble and Dive. They move the same amount of Spaces as you and must also end their movement within 1 Space of you.</p>",
                "format": 1
            },
            "title": {
                "level": 3,
                "show": true
            },
            "type": "text",
