                "controls": true,
                "volume": 0.5
            }
        },
        {
            "_id": "f0e13fff4eed722e",
            "_key": "!journal.pages!31bbf83392ea17cc.f0e13fff4eed722e",
            "_stats": {
                "compodiumSource": null,
                "coreVersion": "12.327",
                "createdTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "duplicateSource": null,
                "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y",
                "modifiedTime": 1721371035.355543,
                "systemId": "dc20rpg",
                "systemVersion": "0.8.0"
            },
            "flags": {},
            "image": {},
            "name": "Volley",
            "ownership": {
                "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3,
                "default": -1
            },
            "sort": 15,
            "src": null,
            "system": {},
            "text": {
                "content": "<p><strong>Requires:</strong> Ranged Weapon</p><p>You can spend<strong> 2 AP </strong>and <strong>1 SP </strong>to launch a volley of projectiles. Choose a point within your Weapon\u2019s range. Make a single Attack Check and compare it against the PD of all creatures of your choice within 1 Space of the chosen point. <strong>Attack Hit:</strong> You deal <strong>2</strong> damage of the Weapon\u2019s type to each creature.</p><p><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong> <strong><em>Impairing Volley:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>1 SP</strong> to cause You can spend 1 SP to force each creature within the area to make a Physical Save against your Save DC. <strong>Failure:</strong> It\u2019s <strong>Impaired</strong> (DisADV on Physical Checks) until the end of your next turn.</p><p><strong><em>Blanket of Arrows:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>1 SP</strong> to increase the area to 3 Spaces from the chosen point.</p><p><strong><em>Line of Arrows:</em></strong> You can spend <strong>1 SP</strong> to also target each creature occupying a Space in a Line between you and the chosen point.</p>",
                "format": 1
